14	// @ax/session-postgres
15	//
16	// Postgres-backed peer of @ax/session-inmemory. Same five service hooks,
17	// same observable contract — only the storage differs.
18	//
19	// Why this plugin takes its own connectionString instead of reaching the
20	// shared pool via `database:get-instance`:
